{"type": "article", "id": 4921, "title": "DC 漫画为主题钢笔", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-05T08:00:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233445FOZqX5VmkS1MduNW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t意大利高端钢笔品牌 Montegrappa 近日推出一系列以 DC 漫画为主题的“英雄与恶棍”系列高端笔，超人、蝙蝠侠、神奇女侠以及绿灯侠 4 个正派角色与猫女、小丑、企鹅人以及谜语人 4 个反派角色均出现在了 Montegrappa 的笔杆上。每一款笔不仅在配色上与其漫画形象保持一致，在笔帽夹的位置还设计了小巧的角色形象与 logo，趣味十足。当然，这一漫画系列也售价不菲，钢笔款定价 475 美元（约合人民币 2947 元），滚珠笔款定价 435 美元（约合人民币 2699 元），圆珠笔款定价 395 美元（约合人民币 2451 元）。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052334421YijonFbzmyS52gW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233442pexVwYikNt1zl2FB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052334439Zcwk6HjMizCNg5e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233443rNEMGCg9LZjBoSde.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233443WJZeEPR2jvdxSAbK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233444ZnVfwqKoglF4YpXd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233444QteU2RJOrh3EjifN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052334447m5CEAfgdRFW2NsI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}